    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>飞行的感觉太棒了！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学习起来很容易，但要掌握却很难。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/03e5325813cc4136e8a46f7cb88a423a.poster.avif?t=1763122026\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/03e5325813cc4136e8a46f7cb88a423a.webm?t=1763122026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每一次碰撞都令人捧腹！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>没有生命值条！</strong><br>无论发生什么，乌鸦总是准备好再次站起来，继续它的旅程。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/60655d29aaba878ede74b35044460785.poster.avif?t=1763122026\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/60655d29aaba878ede74b35044460785.webm?t=1763122026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索一个受北欧神话启发、充满秘密的开放世界！</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/3371676d0b9ff7224579b0aaa3c14ad1.poster.avif?t=1763122026\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/3371676d0b9ff7224579b0aaa3c14ad1.webm?t=1763122026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>学习新的能力——释放雷电、表演空中特技，还有更多精彩！</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/317a0268f74f20a4aa905f12ca88849b.poster.avif?t=1763122026\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/317a0268f74f20a4aa905f12ca88849b.webm?t=1763122026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>解开谜题并挑战试炼！</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/c2ee552f7f032fe079329f238ae44335.poster.avif?t=1763122026\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/c2ee552f7f032fe079329f238ae44335.webm?t=1763122026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>帮助你的家人和朋友！</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/ddfa51946a3316128464bb4be872259b.poster.avif?t=1763122026\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245180/extras/ddfa51946a3316128464bb4be872259b.webm?t=1763122026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>这个故事讲的是什么？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追随一只乌鸦的旅程——从它第一次振翅飞翔到生命的终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死后，每个灵魂都必须抵达“众神之界”——这是法则。<br>但如果一个灵魂无法离开人类世界呢？在这种情况下，乌鸦会引导迷失的灵魂——而现在，这就是你的使命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在前往众神之界的旅途中，你和家人遭到古老邪恶力量的袭击并被分散。<br>帮助每个灵魂，了解他们的故事，找出他们被困的原因，找到你所爱的人，并在世界终结前抵达众神之界。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择属于你自己的道路——多个结局等待你探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: right\"><i>随时流或制作关于游戏的视频-我很荣幸看到您的内容！ <br>如果你需要我的许可，你有它。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>准备好展翅高飞了吗？</strong></h2>",
